## Required Imports (add to view_imports.dart)
```dart
import 'dart:async';
import 'package:rxdart/rxdart.dart';
```

---

## Pre-Delivery Checklist
```
□ Search bar uses DefaultTextField (NOT Container + Text)
□ TextEditingController created & disposed properly
□ PublishSubject for debounce created & closed in dispose
□ StreamSubscription created in initState, cancelled in dispose
□ debounceTime = 500ms + .distinct()
□ Cubit has search() method or accepts search param
□ Query passed as 'search' in queryParameters
□ Widget is StatefulWidget (lifecycle management)
□ Visual style matches Figma (fillColor, borderRadius, prefixIcon)
□ dart:async and rxdart imported in view_imports.dart
```
